snippet.title: Firing Vibes - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1169760/Firing_Vibes/
Discord channel: https://invite.gg/firingvibes

In Firing Vibes, music is your gun.
Destroy your ennemies and bring the Ray to your goal to win in this multiplayer FPS for PC, coming soon on Steam.

Developer: BOING BOING GAMES, indie studio based in France
Music by Aleksandar Alex Djordjevic, Fidelity Production studio
